## cdclients Fields
- selectableVariant (string): "default" or "xDemo" 
- sortOrder (number)
- title (string): Title for the section
- subtitle (string): Optional short tagline
- clientsList (array of objects): Each has:
  - name (string)
  - link (url)
  - logo (image)

## Additional Notes
The fields were derived from the example images and the typical approach for listing logos or partner items.